Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.78,0:18:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fscx120\fscy120\c&H3012C9&\3c&H000000&\4c&H32099B\bord4\shad5}身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnBankGothic Md BT\fscx120\fscy120\3c&H3012C9&\4c&H32099B&\bord4\shad5}Accel
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.26,0:18:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,這就是 照井刑警所變身的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.46,0:18:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,風都的另一名假面騎士
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,假面騎士Accel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.80,0:19:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,自己變成摩托車了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,原來那不是寫錯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.16,0:19:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.84,0:19:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我會坐Revol Garry追上去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.55,0:19:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,一口氣甩開吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,這不是Alcohol的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.73,0:19:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,還有其他參雜體在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:19:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,時芽？照井！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,這些傢伙 不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.54,0:20:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,他們似乎都沒有心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,樣子跟博物館的量產參雜體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和Masquerade非常相似
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.98,0:20:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,博物館…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.54,0:20:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,過去開發蓋亞記憶體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,並把風都作為試驗都市 從在暗地裡支配的組織名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.09,0:20:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,博物館…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.64,0:20:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,感覺好像在哪裡聽過…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我感覺到 很強的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.86,0:20:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,在屋子裡面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.64,0:20:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.74,0:20:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.73,0:20:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人的攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕是將超高頻聲波作為直線發射的招數
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是肉體被打到 恐怕早就粉身碎骨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.30,0:20:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 菲利普
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:20:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是沒見過的驅動器
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,新的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,敵對組織！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.57,0:21:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,左 菲利普
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你們去追真正的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.42,0:21:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就由我 來當這傢伙的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.09,0:21:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,交給你了 照井
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.12,0:21:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,小心剛才的超高頻聲波
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,這種東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.12,0:21:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,在中招前打倒就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.87,0:21:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,絕望！就是你們的終點！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.11,0:21:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來就輪到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,喜歡！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.95,0:21:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不僅是從嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.60,0:21:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,從身上也發出了超音波…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.72,0:21:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,好強 好喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.84,0:22:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,能把你這種強大的人撕碎 我更喜歡！
